  "title": "QC Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><p>·       You are required to perform checks, prepare quality reports, and lead regular meetings with Clients, Consultants and sub-contractor.</p><p>·       Responsible for establishment and implementation of Project's quality control system for MEP services construction activities executed by direct hire and subcontractor personnel.</p><p>·       Supervise inspection activities performed by Quality Control (QC) and Field Engineers, in accordance with the Project Construction QC Plan.</p><p>·       Supervise and coordinate the inspection and testing activities performed by Material Testing and Inspection subcontractor.</p><p>·       Perform Quality Audits on office and site records.</p><p>·       Monitor the progress and effectiveness of the project quality management system.</p><p>·       Recommend and implement improvements when required.</p><p>·       Ensure construction process implementation as per approved methodology & correct\ntesting procedure as per approved ITP.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>·       Minimum 5-year experience of Quality Control matters.</p><p>·        LTA Project Experience is preferred</p><p>·        Singaporean/PR preferred.</p>",
